  "texts": [
    "However, the user interface of the Baseline group presents a linear conversation between the participant and the chatbot with only texts.",
    "The visual representation quickly diverges from the participants' mental model as they go deeper into the sensemaking hierarchy.",
    "On the other hand, the graphical representation of the HINTs system is consistent with the participants' mental model, helping them keep track of their progress by reminding them of their current status and expected subsequent actions.",
    "Second, even though LLMs are powerful chatbots, many of their unresolved issues distract users from their sensemaking of the visualization subfield.",
    "For example, LLMs give answers that are too general in most cases."
